  "text": "One RCT compared a low-calorie version of HMR with counselling [CITATION_1] . No trials continued to 12 months. At obesity reviews 6 months, HMR significantly reduced fasting glucose 0.58 mmol/L more than counselling (ROB: high) ( Fig. 4) . We identified no trials of OPTIFAST in patients without T2DM who met our inclusion criteria.",
